snippet.title: Survival Messenger Adventure
snippet.description:
You wake up with a cramp starting in your left toe and sand in your
mouth.  What has happened you can not remember.  Wind brings a salty
breeze and on an island nobody else is there.

This is the beginning of an interactive fiction game for the Commodore
C64 written by The 7th Division (T7D) and Vintage Computing Carinthia
(VCC) released at the Assembly 2020.

Download from: https://csdb.dk/release/?id=196610
